name: In re REAPPOINTMENT TO DISCIPLINARY BOARD

parties: In re REAPPOINTMENT TO DISCIPLINARY BOARD.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM:
AND NOW, this 12th day of May, 1993, Penina K. Lieber, Esquire, Allegheny County, is reappointed as a member of the Disciplinary Board for a term of three years commencing May 17, 1993.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM:
